{"tid":1294390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 學 術 撚 ] 警察係咪鬼上身?? 驅鬼救港","createTime":"2019-07-07T18:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T18:41:42.000Z","uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"018fc385960d049bbdca33917fe23610712a3868","tid":1294390,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:41:42.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong>(證據一)</strong></ins><br />\n子華神講過<br />\n[[ 我覺得講得出「我好鍾意返工」呢句說話既人，一定係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鬼上身</span></span>。]] (兒童不宜, 2006) <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fIYdcaxqJqg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfIYdcaxqJqg&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=43fbbad2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fIYdcaxqJqg</a><br />\n<br />\n大家唔會忘記佢用行動去表達對返工既熱誠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dN54hDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdN54hDQ.jpg&h=4b5fb5ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>(證據二)</strong></ins><br />\n根據警察通例<br />\n[[<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">便衣人員</span></span>不論是否當值，在與巿民接觸和行使警察權力時，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必須表明身分及出示委任證</span></span>。]]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/waiwai-11_8mmDT_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fwaiwai-11_8mmDT_1200x0.png&h=e65c484c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上中元節臨近, 鬼門大開, 可見鬼上身之說並非空穴來風<br />\n<br />\n除左唱聖詩之外, 仲有冇唔同宗教既教友, <br />\n分享驅鬼方法 / 分辨被附身既症狀以保闔家平安<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tffoyow.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftffoyow.png&h=5ea656a3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}